rComments: This prof is absolutely amazing and loves helping students. She made the class enjoyable and often told us stories of her travels, which really connected with the content we were learning. I loved her lectures because she encouraged students to think from different perspectives and to voice their opinions. Her grading criteria is extremely clear.
Great teacher! Very straight forward and tries to make things as interesting a possible!
Professor Besco was really a great teacher who went out of her way to explain incredibly confusing topics.
